00:39:26.895 --> 00:39:29.880
It gives them arguments
to then speak to other

00:39:29.880 --> 00:39:32.870
politicians who makes
the regulation.

00:39:32.870 --> 00:39:36.170
ALAN EUSTACE: Mark has some
questions from the Dory.

00:39:36.170 --> 00:39:37.970
AUDIENCE: First of
all, [FRENCH].

00:39:37.970 --> 00:39:40.900
Thank you for having spent
