drugs to keep you awake

00:39:51.210 --> 00:39:52.620
that you're not supposed
to take as a pilot?

00:39:52.620 --> 00:39:55.940
Or how are you planning to stay
awake besides just sheer

00:39:55.940 --> 00:39:57.510
excitement?

00:39:57.510 --> 00:39:59.490
ANDRE BORSCHBERG: So we tried,
as I tried to explain at the

00:39:59.490 --> 00:40:01.780
beginning, to make these
pilots sustainable.

00:40:01.780 --> 00:40:05.920
And sustainability is really
a lot of perspective.

00:40:05.920 --> 00:40:08.410
